    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为MTDome的GUI设计一个类图。核心想法是：有一个通用的TabTemplate作为基础，然后TabSelector继承它，同时TabSelector会组合一个Model来处理数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabTemplate",
        "TabSelector",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。TabTemplate放在guitool命名空间里对吧？那Model是放在mtdomegui命名空间吗？还有，TabSelector和Model之间是组合关系还是普通关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "mtdomegui",
        "TabTemplate",
        "Model",
        "TabSelector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TabTemplate在guitool里，Model在mtdomegui里。TabSelector和Model是组合关系，Model的生命周期由TabSelector管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "mtdomegui",
        "TabSelector",
        "Model"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出两个命名空间guitool和mtdomegui，把TabTemplate放进guitool，Model放进mtdomegui，然后建立继承和组合关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "guitool",
        "mtdomegui",
        "TabTemplate",
        "Model",
        "TabSelector"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等一下，TabSelector的位置我没说清楚——它应该也在mtdomegui命名空间里，虽然它继承自guitool的TabTemplate。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabSelector",
        "mtdomegui"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "了解，TabSelector放在mtdomegui命名空间，但继承箭头指向guitool里的TabTemplate。这样跨命名空间的继承关系就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TabSelector",
